quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  20,114,"Ubutungane ni ubwa Allah, Umwami w’ukuri. Bityo (yewe Muhamadi) ntukagire ubwira (mu kwakira) Qur’anmbere y’uko kuyiguhishurira birangira. Ahubwo ujye uvuga uti \"Nyagasani wanjye! Nyongerera ubumenyi"
  20,115,"Kandi rwose mbere twari twarahaye Adamu isezerano (ryo kutarya ku giti cyo mu ijuru), ariko yaribagiwe (akiryaho), dusanga atarazirikanye (isezerano ryacu)"
  20,116,"Unibuke ubwo twabwiraga abamalayika tuti \"Mwubamire Adamu!\" Nuko barubama, uretse Ibilisi (Shitani) wabyanze"
  20,117,"Nuko turavuga tuti \"Yewe Adamu! Mu by’ukuri, uyu ni umwanzi wawe, wowe n’umugore wawe. Bityo, muramenye ntazabakure mu ijuru mutazavaho mukagorwa"
  20,118,"Mu by’ukuri, nta nzara uzarigiriramo ndetse nta n’ubwo uzariburiramo icyo kwambara"
  20,119,Kandinta nyota uzarigiriramo ndetse nta n’ubwo uzicwa n’izuba
  20,120,"Nuko shitani imwoshya igira iti \"Yewe Adamu! Ese nkurangire igiti (waryaho) ukazabaho iteka ndetse (ukazanagira) ubwami budashira"
  20,121,"Nuko bombi (Adamu na Hawa) bakiryaho maze ubwambure bwabo bujya ahagaragara, bityo batangira kubutwikirizaamababi (y’ibiti) byo mu busitani bwo mu Ijuru. Nuko Adamu aba yigometse kuri Nyagasaniwe, maze arayoba"
  20,122,"Hanyuma Nyagasani we aramutoranya, yakira ukwicuza kwe aranamuyobora"
  20,123,"(Allah) aravuga ati \"Nimumanuke mwembi murivemo (mujye ku isi), bamwe bazaba abanzi b’abandi (abantu bazaba abanzi ba Shitani, ndetse na we abe umwanzi wa bo). Kandi umuyoboro wanjye nuramuka ubagezeho, uzakurikira uwo muyoboro wanjye ntazigera ayoba cyangwa ngo agorwe"
  20,124,"Ariko uzirengagiza urwibutso rwanjye, mu by’ukuri, azagira ubuzima bw’inzitanendetse no ku munsi w’imperukatuzamuzura ari impumyi"
  20,125,"Azavuga ati \"Nyagasani wanjye! Ni kuki unzuye ndi impumyi kandi (ku isi) narabonaga"